---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div
  class="rubik_font text-white flex justify-start items-center p-5 flex-col mt-5"
  id="about_me_section"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center max-w-[800px]">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl">
        About me<span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5">. </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-balance">
        I'm <span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >Ariano Alban</span
        >, a <span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >junior Full Stack developer</span
        >
        passionate about technology and continuous learning. I specialize in creating
        <span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >innovative solutions</span
        > in both frontend and backend, and I enjoy exploring new tools and technologies
        to optimize each project. In addition to my technical skills, I possess strong
        soft skills such as <span
          class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >effective communication</span
        >,
        <span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >teamwork</span
        >, and
        <span class="text-primary-10 dark:text-primary-5 font-bold"
          >problem-solving</span
        >, which enable me to adapt and collaborate
        <span class="text-[#c47909] dark:text-[#fdb548] font-bold"
          >efficiently in dynamic</span
        >,
        <span class="text-[#c47909] dark:text-[#fdb548] font-bold"
          >results-oriented work environments</span
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Image
      height="240"
      width="240"
      src="/dev.webp"
      alt="dev"
      class="sm:size-80 size-60"
      loading="lazy"
      title="Ariano Alban Dev Icon"
    />
  </div>
</div>
